sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant API as Booking Controller
    participant BSVC as Booking Service
    participant SSVC as Slot Service
    participant SHSVC as SlotHold Service
    participant PSVC as Payment Service
    participant PW as Payment Webhook
    participant DB as Database
    participant Q as BullMQ Queue
    participant WS as WebSocket Gateway
    participant PG as Payment Gateway

    Note over C,WS: Step 1 - Check Availability
    C->>API: GET /providers/:id/slots?date=2026-04-15
    API->>SSVC: getAvailableSlots(providerId, date)
    SSVC->>DB: load ProviderSchedule
    SSVC->>DB: load ProviderBreaks
    SSVC->>DB: load existing Bookings
    SSVC->>DB: load active SlotHolds
    SSVC->>SSVC: calculate free slots
    SSVC-->>C: [{startTime, endTime, available}]

    Note over C,WS: Step 2 - Hold Slot
    C->>API: POST /bookings/hold {providerId, serviceId, startTime, endTime}
    API->>SHSVC: holdSlot(dto, userId)
    SHSVC->>DB: check slot still available
    SHSVC->>DB: create SlotHold (expiresAt = now + 15min)
    SHSVC-->>C: {holdId, expiresAt}

    Note over C,WS: Step 3 - Create Booking
    C->>API: POST /bookings {providerId, serviceId, startTime, endTime, holdId}
    API->>BSVC: createBooking(dto, userId)
    BSVC->>DB: verify SlotHold exists and not expired
    BSVC->>DB: check cancellation policy
    BSVC->>DB: create Booking (PENDING)
    BSVC->>DB: log status change to STATUS_LOG
    BSVC->>DB: mark SlotHold as converted
    BSVC->>Q: enqueue booking confirmation notification
    BSVC->>WS: broadcast new booking event
    BSVC-->>C: {booking, status: PENDING}

    Note over C,WS: Step 4 - Confirm Booking
    C->>API: PATCH /bookings/:id/status {status: CONFIRMED}
    API->>BSVC: updateStatus(bookingId, status)
    BSVC->>DB: validate status transition
    BSVC->>DB: update Booking status
    BSVC->>DB: log status change to STATUS_LOG
    BSVC->>Q: enqueue confirmation notification
    BSVC->>WS: broadcast booking confirmed event
    BSVC-->>C: {booking, status: CONFIRMED}

    Note over C,WS: Step 5 - Payment
    C->>API: POST /bookings/:id/payments {method: E_WALLET}
    API->>PSVC: create payment
    PSVC->>DB: create Payment (PENDING)
    PSVC->>PG: call payment gateway
    PG-->>PSVC: payment URL
    PSVC-->>C: {paymentUrl}

    Note over C,WS: Step 6 - Payment Webhook
    PG->>PW: POST /payments/webhook {transaction_status, order_id}
    PW->>PG: verify signature
    PW->>DB: update Payment status
    PW->>DB: update Booking (if paid then CONFIRMED)
    PW->>Q: enqueue payment receipt notification
    PW->>WS: broadcast payment received event
    PW-->>PG: {status: OK}
